name: Surrender, Trust, Release
description:
This is a full mix of a 6 track EP that I released the other night. All is produced, mixed, and mastered by myself. It is tuned in entirety to 528 Hz, and it is created with the intention to help the Solar Plexus Chakra chill tf out. Please sit back and enjoy! Much love!
Tracklist:
1. Ahamkara
2. Temperance
3. Sent To Kill
4. Running With Eagle
5. Emotion
6. Avenger
